GetBucket.name: GetBucket

                                                bucket

Grants permission to return the lifecycle configuration information set on an Amazon
                                                S3 bucket

GetObjectTagging.description: Grants permission to return the tag set of an object

ListBucket.description:

                                                1000)

ListBucketMultipartUploads.description: Grants permission to list in-progress multipart uploads

ListMultipartUploadParts.description:
Grants permission to list the parts that have been uploaded for a specific multipart
                                                upload

ListRegionalBuckets.description: Grants permission to list all buckets owned by the authenticated sender of the request

Grants permission to create a new lifecycle configuration for the bucket or replace
                                                an existing lifecycle configuration

PutObject.name: PutObject
PutObject.description: Grants permission to add an object to a bucket

PutObjectAcl.description:
Grants permission to set the access control list (ACL) permissions for an object that
                                                already exists in a bucket

PutObjectTagging.name: PutObjectTagging
PutObjectTagging.description:
Grants permission to set the supplied tag-set to an object that already exists in
                                                a bucket
